    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that's easy on the wallet? This vehicle is a solid performer that still has plenty of miles to go! It shows some honest character and signs of use from its time on the road, but it remains a practical and reliable choice for anyone needing a functional car at a great price. Perfect for a first car or a daily commuter!",
