    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. The exterior has significant rust, multiple dents, and fading paint, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear, including torn upholstery. Mechanically, the engine requires a major overhaul and the transmission is slipping, so it is currently not in reliable driving condition. Please expect to invest significant time and resources into repairs if you plan to get it back on the road.",
